[34m│[0m - `__destruct()` - Called when object is destroyed                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__wakeup()` - Called when object is unserialized                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__toString()` - Called when object is used as string                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__call()` - Called for inaccessible methods                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Tool: phpggc (PHP Generic Gadget Chains)**                                 [34m│[0m
