[32m│[0m === Application Pages ===                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - /list: Shows "No URLs added in your bookmark" with empty list              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - /add: Form with fields "name" and "url" (type="text" and type="url")       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - /about: Static content about the bookmark application                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
