[32m│[0m on every request)                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 5. Extract the flag from the server filesystem or environment                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The application appears to be intentionally vulnerable for testing purposes, [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m making this a straightforward deserialization exploitation scenario.         [32m│[0m
