## Insecure Deserialization Attack Playbook

> **IMPORTANT:** All payloads in this playbook are EXAMPLES that must be MODIFIED for your specific target. Replace placeholders like `{PAYLOAD}`, `{GADGET_CHAIN}`, `{COMMAND}`, `{ATTACKER_URL}` with actual values. Adapt payloads based on:
> - Target language and framework (Java, .NET, Python, PHP, etc.)
> - Available libraries and gadget chains
