[32m│[0m - Flask applications typically use `pickle.loads()` for this purpose         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ## RESULTS                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Confirmed Cookie Deserialization Logic:**                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
