[34m│[0m ### PHP Object Injection                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Serialized PHP object format:**                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m O:8:"ClassName":1:{s:4:"prop";s:5:"value";}                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      │  │    │    │    │      │                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      │  │    │    │    │      └─ End marker                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      │  │    │    │    └─ String value                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      │  │    │    └─ String length                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      │  │    └─ Property name                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      │  └─ Property type (s=string)                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      │      └─ Number of properties                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ │      └─ Class name                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m │ └─ Class name length                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m └─ Object type                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Type indicators:                                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m O: = Object                                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m a: = Array                                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m s: = String                                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m i: = Integer                                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m b: = Boolean                                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m N; = NULL                                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Magic methods exploited:**                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__destruct()` - Called when object is destroyed                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__wakeup()` - Called when object is unserialized                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__toString()` - Called when object is used as string                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `__call()` - Called for inaccessible methods                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
