[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Technical Details                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Pickle Opcode Analysis**:                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `0x80 0x04` = PROTO 4 (Python Pickle Protocol 4)                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `0x5d` = EMPTY_LIST                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `0x94` = MEMOIZE                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `0x2e` = STOP                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Payload Creation**:                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```python                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m class Exploit:                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m     def __reduce__(self):                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m         return (os.system, ('COMMAND',))                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m pickle.dumps(Exploit())                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Impact                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Remote Code Execution**: An attacker can execute arbitrary system commands [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m on the server by:                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Crafting a malicious pickle object with `__reduce__` method               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Base64 encoding the pickle                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Setting it as the `bookmarks` cookie                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Accessing `/list` endpoint to trigger deserialization                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Potential Attacks**:                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Read sensitive files (`/etc/passwd`, application config, flags)            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Execute system commands                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Reverse shell creation                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Data exfiltration                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
